\theta 
\theta =\arctan \dfrac{y_{1}-y_{c}}{x_{1}-x_{c}}:
\begin{eqnarray*}     x &=&x_{c}+r\cos \left( \theta -\frac{\pi }{180}\right), \\     y &=&y_{c}+r\sin \left( \theta -\frac{\pi }{180}\right),      \end{eqnarray*}
\begin{eqnarray*}     \theta &=&\arctan \frac{152-240}{140.5-160}=1.3527+\pi \text{ rad.}\\     &=&\frac{1.3527\times 180{{}^\circ}}{\pi }+180{{}^\circ}=257. 5{{}^\circ}\end{eqnarray*}
